title: Average retail price for eggs in Canada 2019
summary: This graph shows the Average retail price of eggs measured in dollars per dozen for each Month of the year 2019 in Canada .
The lowest price point was in March and the highest price was in September .
gold: The chart shows the trend of the average retail price for eggs in Canada during 2019 . This graph offers an overall upward trend , especially from March to October , with the value 0.26 dollars more than the previous . The average retail price only decreased from February to March , and from October to November .
